NMAP(https://www.freecodecamp.org/news/what-is-nmap-and-how-to-use-it-a-tutorial-for-the-greatest-scanning-tool-of-all-time/)
nmap www.xxx.xxx > scan for open ports and services
nmap --top-ports (x) www.xxx.xxx > scan for first x open ports and services
nmap -sV www.xxx.xxx > Scan with service versions
nmap -A www.xxx.xxx > Scan with Public Key
nmap -p (x) www.xxx.xxx > Scan for particular x port
nmap -iL /input_ips.txt > Large number of IP in that txt file
nmap -oN/oX output.txt/.xml scanme.nmap.org > export output as txt or xml

GOBUSTER(https://hackertargert.com/gobuster-tutorial)
gobuster version > Version
gobuster dir -u https://xxxx -w [WordListPATH]/xxx.txt -t x(int) --delay x(int)s -x (.php,.txt)> Find linked pages and portals 
-u(WebsiteAddress), -w(Wordlist), -t(No. of words), -x(Particular Extension)
